65
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:04,580
that's one of the
keys to startup.

66
00:03:04,580 --> 00:03:06,120
The second is secrecy.

67
00:03:06,120 --> 00:03:11,460
Maybe nobody else knows
exactly how you do what you do.

68
00:03:11,460 --> 00:03:12,540
The third is speed.

69
00:03:12,540 --> 00:03:14,950
Even with that other stuff
you need to move quickly.

70
00:03:14,950 --> 00:03:17,740
And that could be a real
key advantage-- an idea.

71
00:03:17,740 --> 00:03:19,177
And the fourth
thing-- in thinking

72
00:03:19,177 --> 00:03:21,010
