1170
00:55:10,010 --> 00:55:11,860
and you've got to
hire in some people.

1171
00:55:11,860 --> 00:55:14,470
But that's a reasonable
rule of thumb.

1172
00:55:14,470 --> 00:55:16,610
And for most equity
plans, you're

